      <title>津巴布韦将宣布本币暴跌 73% 后的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/gold-standard-beckons-zimbabwe-dollar-as-new-governor-set-to-reveal-new-policy</link>
